qualifier.query:
SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 
            FROM XFHISTORIAN.SESNUMBERS 
            WHERE OPERATING_MODE = 'MANUAL' 
              AND STATUS = 'N'
        ) THEN 1 
        ELSE 0 
    END AS Found
FROM dual
